== [http://pingus.seul.org/ Pingus] ==
[[File:Pingus_screenshot1.png|thumb|right|200px]]
Pingus is a free clone of the popular Lemmings game. Your goal is to guide a horde of penguins through a world full of obstacles and penguin traps to safety. Although penguins (unlike lemmings) are rather smart, they sometimes lack the necessary overview and now rely on you to save them.

